{"tid":1523773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"警方嚴厲譴責激進示威者在港鐵內暴力行為","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T16:31:49.000Z","uid":66357,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"9d93f94ad2ae538555c50e7f6f100bba52e4ab33","tid":1523773,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:09:35.000Z","msg":"電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n  有激進暴力示威者，在港鐵旺角站衝擊客戶服務中心及毀壞售票機。<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者亦在港鐵太子站內襲擊市民，毀壞站內設施。</span><br />\n   <br />\n  警方接報進入港鐵範圍制止暴力行為及拘捕違法者，呼籲在場市民立即離開。<br />\n   <br />\n  警方對示威者一切暴力行為，予以嚴厲譴責。<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月31日（星期六）<br />\n香港時間23時52分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a60f0510def43426a536985f87505fc570d224b9","tid":1523773,"uid":66357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"618fea55f1a091347a916c7a24e8002717944729","tid":1523773,"uid":168057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:11:22.000Z","msg":"831 香港警察無差別攻擊市民"},{"pid":"401a8c12aeafcbe6a2cb2e19a540f0f68b737a73","tid":1523773,"uid":54126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"食屎啦黑警 顛倒是非<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18723292a605